text: Þis synt þa landgemæra to cunictune.

Ærest of bugla fenne &lang þa riscweges on eneda wylle þonon on þone mere of þam mere on holan broc &lang broces to upwylle þonon to glædtuninga wege of þam wege on earninga stræte þonon on seaxa broc &lang broces on gyruwan fen þa eft on bugla fen.
Þis is þara IX hida boc æt Cunictune þe Eadwig cing gebocode Wulfstane his þegne on ece yrfe.
